# Now find a suitable location for the lock. A lock requires two full flat tiles connected by a single slope.<br/>[[File:en/Kanalen 3-2.png|frame|none|Een geschikte plaats voor een sluis.]]
# Click on the slope to build the lock.<br/>[[File:en/Manual/Building-canals-3.png|frame|none|The lock.]]
# Repeat steps 3 and 4 to place more locks if necessary.

